ths that can critically modify their architectures, unlike our\nSolar System which has preserved its planets on nearly circular orbits. This\nstudy also opens to the possibility of using chemical abundances of stars to\nidentify which ones are the most likely to host analogues of the calm Solar\nSystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 2021 21:25:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-30"}
