{and}\\quad\nQ_* = [-1/2+\\delta,1/2-\\delta]^n\\times[-3\\epsilon^2,-2\\epsilon^2].$$ Further,\nwe supply a version of the strong Markov property for caloric measures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 15:15:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-30"}
