 AFM applications. Experiments show indeed a stable closed-loop\noperation with a setpoint of 4 nN/nm for an unprecedented sub-picometer\nvibration amplitude, where the tip-sample interaction is mediated by a\nstretched water meniscus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 07:37:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-07"}
